<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Remplissez votre carnet de chantiers | FluxClients</title>
<style>
  @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Archivo+Expanded:wght@600;700;800&family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700&display=swap');

  :root {
    --navy: #13233B;
    --navy-soft: #1C3050;
    --concrete: #EFECE6;
    --concrete-dim: #E2DED4;
    --orange: #D85C2C;
    --green: #3F7D5C;
    --ink: #1A1A18;
    --paper: #FAF8F4;
  }

  * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }

  html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }

  body {
    background: var(--paper);
    color: var(--ink);
    font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
    line-height: 1.5;
    -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
  }

  .display {
    font-family: 'Archivo Expanded', sans-serif;
    font-weight: 800;
    letter-spacing: -0.01em;
  }

  /* ---------- TOP BAR ---------- */
  .topbar {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
    padding: 22px 6vw;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--concrete-dim);
  }
  .topbar .mark {
    font-family: 'Archivo Expanded', sans-serif;
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 18px;
    color: var(--navy);
    letter-spacing: 0.01em;
  }
  .topbar .mark span { color: var(--orange); }
  .topbar .tag {
    font-size: 12.5px;
    color: var(--navy);
    background: var(--concrete);
    padding: 6px 14px;
    border-radius: 100px;
    border: 1px solid var(--concrete-dim);
  }

  /* ---------- HERO / INTRO ---------- */
  .intro {
    max-width: 760px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 64px 6vw 36px;
    text-align: center;
  }
  .eyebrow {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 8px;
    font-size: 13px;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--green);
    background: rgba(63,125,92,0.08);
    border: 1px solid rgba(63,125,92,0.25);
    padding: 7px 16px;
    border-radius: 100px;
    margin-bottom: 28px;
  }
  .eyebrow .dot {
    width: 7px; height: 7px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: var(--green);
  }
  h1 {
    font-size: clamp(32px, 5vw, 50px);
    line-height: 1.08;
    color: var(--navy);
    margin-bottom: 18px;
  }
  h1 .hl {
    background: linear-gradient(180deg, transparent 62%, rgba(216,92,44,0.22) 62%);
  }
  .intro p {
    font-size: 17px;
    color: #4A4A46;
    max-width: 540px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  /* ---------- VIDEO SECTION ---------- */
  .video-wrap {
    max-width: 920px;
    margin: 8px auto 0;
    padding: 0 6vw;
  }
  .video-frame {
    position: relative;
    border-radius: 14px;
    overflow: hidden;
    background: var(--navy);
    box-shadow: 0 30px 70px -25px rgba(19,35,59,0.45);
    border: 1px solid var(--navy);
  }
  .video-frame::before {
    content: "";
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    border-radius: 14px;
    padding: 1px;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(216,92,44,0.5), transparent 40%);
    -webkit-mask: linear-gradient(#000 0 0) content-box, linear-gradient(#000 0 0);
    -webkit-mask-composite: xor;
    mask-composite: exclude;
    pointer-events: none;
    z-index: 2;
  }
  .video-embed {
    position: relative;
    padding-bottom: 56.25%;
    height: 0;
  }
  .video-embed iframe {
    position: absolute;
    top: 0; left: 0;
    width: 100%; height: 100%;
    border: 0;
  }
  .video-caption {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 10px;
    margin-top: 16px;
    font-size: 13.5px;
    color: #8A8A82;
  }
  .video-caption .pulse {
    width: 6px; height: 6px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: var(--orange);
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  /* ---------- PROOF SECTION (real Meta Ads screenshots) ---------- */
  .proof-section {
    max-width: 760px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 56px 6vw 64px;
  }
  .proof-heading {
    text-align: center;
    font-size: 13px;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: #8A8A82;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.04em;
    margin-bottom: 36px;
  }
  .client-block {
    margin-bottom: 36px;
  }
  .client-block:last-child {
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }
  .client-label {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 10px;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
  }
  .client-number {
    width: 24px;
    height: 24px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: var(--navy);
    color: var(--paper);
    font-size: 12px;
    font-weight: 700;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }
  .client-name {
    font-size: 15px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--navy);
  }
  .client-shot-group {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 10px;
    border-radius: 12px;
    overflow: hidden;
    box-shadow: 0 20px 50px -22px rgba(19,35,59,0.2);
    border: 1px solid var(--concrete-dim);
    background: white;
    padding: 4px;
  }
  .client-shot-group img {
    width: 100%;
    height: auto;
    display: block;
    border-radius: 8px;
  }
  .proof-caption {
    margin-top: 28px;
    font-size: 12.5px;
    color: #8A8A82;
    text-align: center;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  @media (max-width: 640px) {
    .topbar { padding: 18px 5vw; }
    .intro { padding: 44px 5vw 28px; }
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>

  <div class="topbar">
    <div class="mark">Flux<span>Clients</span></div>
  </div>

  <div class="intro">
    <div class="eyebrow"><span class="dot"></span>Pour les entreprises du bâtiment et du renouvellement énergétique</div>
    <h1>Regardez ça <span class="hl">avant qu'on se parle</span></h1>
    <p>Comment on remplit un carnet de chantiers sans dépendre du bouche-à-oreille, avec mes vrais chiffres en direct.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="video-wrap">
    <div class="video-frame">
      <div class="video-embed">
        <iframe src="https://www.loom.com/embed/46954ef09b364a0dbb970d28cf59297c" frameborder="0" webkitallowfullscreen mozallowfullscreen allowfullscreen></iframe>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="video-caption"><span class="pulse"></span>Regardez-la en entier, on gagnera du temps pendant l'appel</div>
  </div>

  <div class="proof-section">
    <div class="proof-heading">Coût par prospect sur nos campagnes en cours</div>

    <div class="client-block">
      <div class="client-label">
        <span class="client-number">1</span>
        <span class="client-name">Client solaire</span>
      </div>
      <div class="client-shot-group">
        <img src="data:image/png;base64," alt="Campagne Meta Ads client solaire : coûts par prospect">
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="client-block">
      <div class="client-label">
        <span class="client-number">2</span>
        <span class="client-name">Client fenêtres</span>
      </div>
      <div class="client-shot-group">
        <img src="data:image/png;base64," alt="Campagne Meta Ads client fenêtres : coûts par prospect">
        <img src="data:image/png;base64," alt="Campagne Meta Ads client fenêtres : coûts par prospect, suite">
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="proof-caption">Données réelles, captures de nos campagnes Meta Ads en cours. Le coût varie selon le secteur et la zone géographique.</div>
  </div>

</body>
</html>
